'''''Slayer''''' is a [[Scrolling shooter|horizontally scrolling shooter]] developed by Imperial Software for the [[Amiga]], [[Atari ST]], and [[Commodore 64]]. [[Hewson Consultants]] published the game in 1988. The game consists of three levels, each with a [[boss (video gaming)|boss]] which must be defeated at the end. [[Power-up]]s such as bonus weapons and shields scattered around the levels.

